column5: We'll be making the drive to the great north. I'm getting soo excited.
I'll be checking into the resort on LOTW and hustling to unpack and get my licence so we can get out on the water!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
http://www.mnr.gov.on.ca/en/Business...02_164832.html Walleye hunter try the on-line link you can print out your license at home, no waiting in line!
I will be in the office wishing I was fishing at this time next week.
